Map Screen
==========

- Don't prompt for position source permission until on screen.
- Display player and asset markers as map objects:
  https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qml-qtlocation-map.html#addMapItem-method
- Zoom to fit all markers when map is initially displayed:
  https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qml-qtlocation-map.html#fitViewportToMapItems-method
- Implement error handling for map plugin errors:
  https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qml-qtlocation-map.html#error-prop
- Indicate off-the-grid markers with special colors:
  https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qtpositioning-qmlmodule.html
- Display assets' navigation plans as waypoints.
